column2: select a.ID, a.Genre_Name, a.Media_Name from (select distinct Track.GenreId as &&&, Genre.GenreId as ID, Genre.Name as Genre_Name, Track.MediaTypeId as &&&, MediaType.MediaTypeId as &&&, MediaType.Name as &&&   From chinook.Track Inner Join chinook.genre on Track.GenreId = Genre.GenreId Inner Join chinook.MediaType on Track.MediaTypeId = MediaType.MediaTypeId) a Order By ID
